    <item>
      <title>英国的凯尔·斯塔默需要抑制他的人工智能热情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-ai-vision-for-the-uk-could-use-a-reality-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加倍加强国家在人工智能方面的强有力监管领导作用，将比追求模糊和不确定的产业政策更为明智。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-ai-vision-for-the-uk-could-use-a-reality-check</guid>
